ier and bridgeman passim  jacobs p   ainger pp –  baily p  ainger p   ainger p   jacobs p   ainger pp –  jacobs p   crowther andrew the carpet quarrel explained the gilbert and sullivan archive accessed  august   ainger p   jacobs pp –  rollins  witts p   mackerness ed cellier alfred grove music online oxford music online accessed  august  subscription required and gänzl kurt cloches de corneville les the new grove dictionary of opera grove music online oxford music online accessed  august   jacobs pp –  turnbull stephen sullivan biography the gilbert and sullivan archive accessed  august   a b c russell hulme david notes to hyperion cd set cda the golden legend   jacobs p   ainger pp –  ainger pp    ainger pp – and jacobs pp –  sir arthur sullivan a talk with the composer of pinafore san francisco chronicle  july  p   hughes p  a b letter from gilbert to sullivan  february  quoted in jacobs p   letter from sullivan to gilbert  march  quoted in jacobs pp –  jacobs pp – and  and ainger p   a b hughes p   ainger p   stedman p   ainger pp –  ainger p   lamb andrew ivanhoe and the royal english opera the musical times vol  no  may  pp –  jacobs pp –  ainger p   a b gordonpowell robin ivanhoe full score introduction vol i pp xii–xiv  the amber ring  eden david ivanhoe on tour  sir arthur sullivan society magazine no  summer   klein herman an account of the composition and production of ivanhoe thirty years of musical life in london –  reprinted at the gilbert and sullivan archive  october  accessed  october   a b jacobs pp –  a b young p   a b eden david and william parry notes to hyperion cd set cda the contrabandista and the foresters   lamb andrew sullivan the contrabandista gramophone december  p   jacobs pp –  jacobs pp –  jacobs pp –  ainger p   ainger p   coles clifton mirette introduction gilbert and sullivan archive  may  accessed october    ainger p   ainger p   young p   jacobs pp –  entry from sullivans diary quoted in jacobs p   jacobs p   coles clifton the 