so with the autograph of another unknown artist dated in  size is  x  inches very good condition also included is a photo print of him sized  x  inches see scans    usd default title   usd sold out pick a currency usd eur cad gbp aud jpy zar hkd all items shown in our website are in stock and prices are final  all guaranteed authentic share this item tweet pin it about us  shipping  privacy  contact us  want to sell  gift cards  whats new  our blog  broadcast copyright   tamino autographs the  autograph dealer of opera classical music film  ballet autographs memorabilia and gifts sullivan arthur  musical score explorermusikmphde sullivan arthur sullivan arthur te deum laudamus boer war te deum with sullivan’s original hymn onward christian soldiers sku  categories choirvoice  orchestra the phillip brookes collection add to cart  € description details sullivan arthur te deum laudamus boer war te deum with sullivan’s original hymn onward christian soldiers the score is introduced with a scholarly preface english and german and the preface is available online for inspection  all this is made possible by a worldwide network of musicians musicologists and musicloving amateurs who contribute to the series in many different ways at the end of the preface you find a reference to the music publisher providing performance materials in case we provide the performance materials you find a note under the additional information tab   read preface  vorwort  here score no  special edition the phillip brookes collection genre choirvoice  orchestra pages  size  x  mm printing reprint related products brahms johannes altrhapsodie op  schicksalslied song of destiny op  nänie nenia op   € no  add to cart details